column21: SELECT  CAST(ACC.M_ENTITY AS CHAR(10)) AS M_ENTITY,  CAST(ACC.M_EN_ACCOUNT AS CHAR(20)) AS M_EN_ACCOUNT,  CAST(ACC.M_EN_AMTC AS NUMBER(24,3)) AS M_EN_AMTC,  CAST(ACC.M_EN_AMTD AS NUMBER(24,3)) AS M_EN_AMTD,  CAST(ACC.M_EN_AMTN AS NUMBER(24,3)) AS M_EN_AMTN,  CAST(ACC.M_EN_CUR AS CHAR(3)) AS M_EN_CUR, CAST(ACC.M_EN_DATE AS DATE) AS M_EN_DATE,   CAST(DTE.M_H_DATE2 AS DATE) AS M_H_DATE2, CAST(DTE.M_H_NXT_DATE AS DATE) AS M_H_NXT_DATE, CAST(ACC.M_H_ACCSEC AS CHAR(20)) AS M_H_ACCSEC,  CAST(ACC.M_H_ACCTYPE AS CHAR(1)) AS M_H_ACCTYPE,  CAST(ACC.M_H_ACC_F2 AS CHAR(2)) AS M_H_ACC_F2, CAST(ACC.M_H_ACC_F3 AS CHAR(3)) AS M_H_ACC_F3, CAST(ACC.M_H_ACC_FD AS CHAR(1)) AS M_H_ACC_FD, CAST(ACC.M_H_AMOUNT AS NUMBER(20,3)) AS M_H_AMOUNT, CAST(ACC.M_H_X_CUR AS CHAR(3)) AS M_H_X_CUR, CAST(CASE WHEN ACC.M_H_X_CUR!='!!!' THEN NVL(FXCV1.M_MID_FACTOR,0) * NVL(ACC.M_H_AMOUNT,0) / NVL(FXCV2.M_MID_FACTOR,0)      ELSE 0 END AS NUMBER(20,3)) AS M_H_X_AMT FROM (     SELECT      BAL.M_ENTITY, BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT, BAL.M_EN_AMTC, BAL.M_EN_AMTD, BAL.M_EN_AMTN, BAL.M_EN_DATE,  INST.M_DSP_LABEL AS M_EN_CUR,     CASE WHEN SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,3,1)='T' THEN 'TRADING'          WHEN SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,3,1)='A' THEN 'AMORTIZED'          ELSE CONCAT(SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,3,1),'-INTERNAL') END AS M_H_ACCSEC,     CASE WHEN BAL.M_EN_AMTN>0 THEN 'D'          ELSE 'C' END AS M_H_ACCTYPE,     SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,1,2) AS M_H_ACC_F2,     SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,1,3) AS M_H_ACC_F3,     SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,4,1) AS M_H_ACC_FD,     ABS(BAL.M_EN_AMTN) AS M_H_AMOUNT,     CASE WHEN SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,1,2)='BD' THEN 'TWD'          WHEN SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,1,2)='BO' THEN 'USD'          WHEN SUBSTR(BAL.M_EN_ACCOUNT,1,2)='HK' THEN 'HKD'          ELSE '!!!' END AS M_H_X_CUR      FROM      TRN_ACJS_DBF BAL, TRN_PLIN_DBF INST     WHERE     BAL.M_INSTRUMENT = INST.M_REFERENCE (+)     AND     BAL.M_EN_DATE =@REPORTINGDATE:D     --BAL.M_EN_DATE = TO_DATE('20120911','YYYYMMDD') ) ACC ,  (     SELECT     HCVB.M_DATE AS M_DATE,     HCVH.M_KEY1 AS M_CURR,     HCVB.M_MID_FACTOR AS M_MID_FACTOR     FROM      BSPB_FX_HBS HCVB, HSPB_FX_H2S HCVH      WHERE      HCVB.M_KEYID=HCVH.M_KEYID (+)     AND     HCVB.M_DATE=@REPORTINGDATE:D     --HCVB.M_DATE=TO_DATE('20120911','YYYYMMDD') ) FXCV1, (     SELECT     HCVB.M_DATE AS M_DATE,     HCVH.M_KEY1 AS M_CURR,     HCVB.M_MID_FACTOR AS M_MID_FACTOR     FROM      BSPB_FX_HBS HCVB, HSPB_FX_H2S HCVH      WHERE      HCVB.M_KEYID=HCVH.M_KEYID (+)     AND     HCVB.M_DATE=@REPORTINGDATE:D     --HCVB.M_DATE=TO_DATE('20120911','YYYYMMDD') ) FXCV2 , (     SELECT @REPORTINGDATE:D AS M_H_DATE2, @REPORTINGNXTBDATE:D AS M_H_NXT_DATE FROM DUAL     --SELECT TO_DATE('20120911','YYYYMMDD') AS M_H_DATE2, TO_DATE('20120912','YYYYMMDD') AS M_H_NXT_DATE FROM DUAL ) DTE WHERE ACC.M_EN_CUR = FXCV1.M_CURR (+) AND ACC.M_H_X_CUR = FXCV2.M_CURR (+) AND ACC.M_EN_DATE = DTE.M_H_DATE2

END AS M_H_X_CUR      FROM      TRN_ACJS_DBF BAL, TRN_PLIN_DBF INST     WHERE     BAL.M_INSTRUMENT = INST.M_REFERENCE (+)     AND     BAL.M_EN_DATE =@REPORTINGDATE:D     --BAL.M_EN_DATE = TO_DATE('20120911','YYYYMMDD') ) ACC ,  (     SELECT     HCVB.M_DATE AS M_DATE,     HCVH.M_KEY1 AS M_CURR,     HCVB.M_MID_FACTOR AS M_MID_FACTOR     FROM      BSPB_FX_HBS HCVB, HSPB_FX_H2S HCVH      WHERE      HCVB.M_KEYID=HCVH.M_KEYID (+)     AND     HCVB.M_DATE=@REPORTINGDATE:D     --HCVB.M_DATE=TO_DATE('20120911','YYYYMMDD') ) FXCV1, (     SELECT     HCVB.M_DATE AS M_DATE,     HCVH.M_KEY1 AS M_CURR,     HCVB.M_MID_FACTOR AS M_MID_FACTOR     FROM      BSPB_FX_HBS HCVB, HSPB_FX_H2S HCVH      WHERE      HCVB.M_KEYID=HCVH.M_KEYID (+)     AND     HCVB.M_DATE=@REPORTINGDATE:D     --HCVB.M_DATE=TO_DATE('20120911','YYYYMMDD') ) FXCV2 , (     SELECT @REPORTINGDATE:D AS M_H_DATE2, @REPORTINGNXTBDATE:D AS M_H_NXT_DATE FROM DUAL     --SELECT TO_DATE('20120911','YYYYMMDD') AS M_H_DATE2, TO_DATE('20120912','YYYYMMDD') AS M_H_NXT_DATE FROM DUAL ) DTE WHERE ACC.M_EN_CUR = FXCV1.M_CURR (+) AND ACC.M_H_X_CUR = FXCV2.M_CURR (+) AND ACC.M_EN_DATE = DTE.M_H_DATE2

column21: SELECT   A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO,   CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%HEDGED%' THEN C.M_RESULTV*A.PERCENTAGE ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2)) AS M_HEDGEDDIFF,   CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%HEDGING%' THEN C.M_RESULTV*A.PERCENTAGE  ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2)) AS M_HEDGINGDIF,   CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%THEORETICAL%' THEN C.M_RESULTV*A.PERCENTAGE  ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2))  AS M_THDIFF     FROM    (  SELECT   E.M_CTN,   F.M_TRADE_OREF,   'HEDGED' AS M_TYPE,  F.M_QUANTITY/F.M_INIT_QTY AS PERCENTAGE  FROM   HEDGE#HDGD_COMPL_DBF E, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF F   WHERE   E.M_REF =F.M_REFERENCE      UNION ALL      SELECT   G.M_CTN,   H.M_TRADE_OREF,   'HEDGING' AS M_TYPE,  H.M_QUANTITY/H.M_INIT_QTY AS PERCENTAGE   FROM  HEDGE#HDGG_COMPL_DBF G, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF H   WHERE   G.M_REF =H.M_REFERENCE      UNION ALL      SELECT   I.M_CTN,   J.M_TRADE_OREF,   'THEORETICAL' AS M_TYPE,  J.M_QUANTITY/J.M_INIT_QTY AS PERCENTAGE   FROM  HEDGE#THEO_COMPL_DBF I, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF J   WHERE   I.M_REF = J.M_REFERENCE  )A, STD#VR_VR1 B, STD#VR_VR2 C     WHERE   B.M_DEALNUM IN (SELECT K.M_NB FROM TRN_HDR_DBF K WHERE K.M_TRN_STATUS <> 'DEAD' AND K.M_MRPL_ONB = A.M_TRADE_OREF)  AND B.M_KEY_ID = C.M_KEY_ID   AND C.M_OTYPE=2  GROUP BY A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO  ORDER BY A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO    /*SELECT  A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO,  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%HEDGED%' THEN C.M_RESULTV ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2)) AS M_HEDGEDDIFF,  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%HEDGING%' THEN C.M_RESULTV ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2)) AS M_HEDGINGDIF,  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%THEORETICAL%' THEN C.M_RESULTV ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2))  AS M_THDIFF  FROM   ( SELECT  E.M_CTN,  F.M_TRADE_OREF,  'HEDGED' AS M_TYPE  FROM  HEDGE#HDGD_COMPL_DBF E, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF F  WHERE  E.M_REF =F.M_REFERENCE   UNION ALL   SELECT  G.M_CTN,  H.M_TRADE_OREF,  'HEDGING' AS M_TYPE  FROM HEDGE#HDGG_COMPL_DBF G, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF H  WHERE  G.M_REF =H.M_REFERENCE   UNION ALL   SELECT  I.M_CTN,  J.M_TRADE_OREF,  'THEORETICAL' AS M_TYPE  FROM HEDGE#THEO_COMPL_DBF I, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF J  WHERE  I.M_REF = J.M_REFERENCE )A, STD#VR_VR1 B, STD#VR_VR2 C  WHERE  A.M_TRADE_OREF = B.M_DEALNUM  AND B.M_KEY_ID = C.M_KEY_ID  AND C.M_OTYPE=2 GROUP BY A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO ORDER BY A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO*/
